#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:32
#: of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"An ndarray is returned with one :class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` per column "
"when ``subplots=True``.      See Also     --------     "
"matplotlib.pyplot.plot : Plot y versus x as lines and/or markers.      "
"Examples     --------      .. plot::         :context: close-figs"
"          >>> import maxframe.tensor as mt         >>> import "
"maxframe.dataframe as md         >>> s = md.Series([1, 3, 2])         >>>"
" s.plot.line()  # doctest: +SKIP      .. plot::         :context: close-"
"figs          The following example shows the populations for some "
"animals         over the years.          >>> df = md.DataFrame({         "
"...    'pig': [20, 18, 489, 675, 1776],         ...    'horse': [4, 25, "
"281, 600, 1900]         ...    }, index=[1990, 1997, 2003, 2009, 2014])"
"         >>> lines = df.plot.line()      .. plot::        :context: "
"close-figs         An example with subplots, so an array of axes is "
"returned.         >>> axes = df.plot.line(subplots=True)        >>> "
"type(axes).execute()        <class 'numpy.ndarray'>      .. plot::"
"        :context: close-figs         Let's repeat the same example, but "
"specifying colors for        each column (in this case, for each animal)."
"         >>> axes = df.plot.line(        ...     subplots=True, "
"color={\"pig\": \"pink\", \"horse\": \"#742802\"}        ... )      .. "
"plot::         :context: close-figs          The following example shows "
"the relationship between both         populations.          >>> lines = "
"df.plot.line(x='pig', y='horse')"
msgstr ""
"当 ``subplots=True`` 时，返回一个 ndarray，每个列对应一个 :class:`"
"matplotlib.axes.Axes`。      另请参阅     --------     matplotlib.pyplot."
"plot : 将 y 与 x 绘制成线条和/或标记。      示例     --------      .. "
"plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> import maxframe.tensor "
"as mt         >>> import maxframe.dataframe as md         >>> s = md."
"Series([1, 3, 2])         >>> s.plot.line()  # doctest: +SKIP      .. "
"plot::         :context: close-figs          以下示例显示了某些动物多年来"
"的人口数量。          >>> df = md.DataFrame({         ...    'pig': [20, "
"18, 489, 675, 1776],         ...    'horse': [4, 25, 281, 600, 1900]     "
"    ...    }, index=[1990, 1997, 2003, 2009, 2014])         >>> lines = "
"df.plot.line()      .. plot::        :context: close-figs         使用"
"子图的示例，返回一个 axes 数组。         >>> axes = df.plot.line(subplots"
"=True)        >>> type(axes).execute()        <class 'numpy.ndarray'>    "
"  .. plot::        :context: close-figs         重复相同的示例，但为每列"
"（在此情况下为每种动物）指定颜色。         >>> axes = df.plot.line(      "
"  ...     subplots=True, color={\"pig\": \"pink\", \"horse\": \"#742802\""
"}        ... )      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          以下"
"示例显示了两个种群之间的关系。          >>> lines = df.plot.line(x='pig',"
" y='horse')"

